                strong State of the Academy
              p Created a <a href = "https://sota.phillipian.net/year/2018/">website</a> of interactive visualizations showing the results of <i>The Phillipian</i>'s State of the Academy survey, an annual survey covering politics, academics, wellness, and culture at my high school. Built with D3.
